#: forms.py:179 models.py:104
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The reCAPTCHA widget supports several <a href=\"{attr_link}\" "
"target=\"_blank\">data attributes</a> that customize the behaviour of the "
"widget, such as <code>data-theme</code>, <code>data-size</code>. The "
"reCAPTCHA api supports several <a href=\"{api_link}\" "
"target=\"_blank\">parameters</a>. Add these api parameters as attributes, "
"e.g. <code>hl</code> to set the language."
msgstr ""
"De reCAPTCHA-widget ondersteunt verschillende <a href=\"{attr_link}\" "
"target=\"_blank\">data-attributen</a> waarmee u het gedrag van de widget "
"kunt aanpassen, zoals <code>data-thema</code> en <code>data-grootte</code>. "
"De reCAPTCHA API ondersteunt verschillende <a href=\"{api_link}\" "
"target=\"_blank\">parameters</a>. Voeg deze API-parameters toe als "
"attributen, bijvoorbeeld <code>hl</code> om de taal in te stellen."

